Most of this is my evolution of playing this game over 1 year now. (430days)

There is a lot here but this is just my scratch paper of things that I have used for this game.

I play the Desktop Steam Version of "Realm Grinder" for Mac.

I honestly never thought I would like a clicker game, but here I am clickin' time to time.
